OL,3,C'A privilege': Arthur Fery's former
OL,4,Ccoach ahead of Wimbledon quarter-final
OL,6,FWATCH: Who is British Wimbledon
OL,7,Fwildcard Arthur Fery?
OL,9,FAfter beating Belgian player Zizou
OL,10,FBergs on Monday, Arthur Fery reached
OL,11,Fthe Wimbledon quarter-finals - his
OL,12,Fbest run at a Grand Slam.
OL,14,FFery attended Stanford University
OL,15,Fbetween 2020-23 on a tennis
OL,16,Fscholarship where he studied for a
OL,17,FScience, Technology and Society degree.
OL,19,FPaul Goldstein, head of men's tennis,
OL,20,Fcoached the 23-year-old throughout his
OL,21,Ftime at the university.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
