OL,3,C'A privilege': Arthur Fery's former
OL,4,Ccoach ahead of Wimbledon quarter-final
OL,6,F"I think there are millions of people
OL,7,Fnow who have seen what a quality
OL,8,Ftennis player he is," he said. "But I
OL,9,Fwant everyone to understand that as
OL,10,Fgood of a tennis player as he is. He's
OL,11,Fa better human being."
OL,13,FDespite Arthur's success on the court
OL,14,Fin his teens, he made the decision to
OL,15,Fpursue academics alongside his tennis
OL,16,Fequally.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
