OL,3,C'A privilege': Arthur Fery's former
OL,4,Ccoach ahead of Wimbledon quarter-final
OL,6,F"Many of his tennis peers were
OL,7,Fprobably prioritising tennis at the
OL,8,Fexpense of academics and he was trying
OL,9,Fto pursue both simultaneously," Paul
OL,10,Ftold ITV News.
OL,12,F"When we recruited him for Stanford,
OL,13,Fhe was probably a little bit more
OL,14,Funder the radar than he should have
OL,15,Fbeen given his abilities.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
