PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1783703991
OL,3,C'A privilege': Arthur Fery's former
OL,4,Ccoach ahead of Wimbledon quarter-final
OL,6,F"He plays the game with an
OL,7,Fexceptionally high IQ. His tennis IQ
OL,8,Fis off the charts but he has interests
OL,9,Foutside the sport, he has
OL,10,Frelationships outside the sport that
OL,11,Fare meaningful and important."
OL,13,FFery is the only remaining British
OL,14,Fplayer in the singles draw at
OL,15,FWimbledon.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
