PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1783703991
OL,3,C'A privilege': Arthur Fery's former
OL,4,Ccoach ahead of Wimbledon quarter-final
OL,6,F"He is a quality human being who has
OL,7,Fearned and deserves this wonderful
OL,8,Fmoment that he's having, moments that
OL,9,Fhe is having and he's handling it so
OL,10,Fimpressively - with humility, with
OL,11,Fexcellence, and he's representing
OL,12,Fhimself, his family, his former
OL,13,Fschool, you name it, so incredibly
OL,14,Fwell.
OL,16,F"You just can't help but feel anything
OL,17,Fbut the greatest joy for him. It is so
OL,18,Fwell deserved, and it could not happen
OL,19,Fto a better person. And so it's just
OL,20,Fan exciting time."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
