OL,3,C'A privilege': Arthur Fery's former
OL,4,Ccoach ahead of Wimbledon quarter-final
OL,6,FStanford university has one of the
OL,7,Fmost successful university tennis
OL,8,Fprogrammes.
OL,10,FStanford Tennis alumni include
OL,11,FAmerican John McEnroe, who went on to
OL,12,Fwin the Wimbledon men's singles grand
OL,13,Fslam three times.
OL,15,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
