OL,3,C'A privilege': Arthur Fery's former
OL,4,Ccoach ahead of Wimbledon quarter-final
OL,6,F"Minutes after Arthur shook hands with
OL,7,FDimitrov the president of our
OL,8,Funiversity wanted Arthur's contact
OL,9,Finformation to be able to congratulate
OL,10,Fhim directly.
OL,12,F"It's thrilling for our university,
OL,13,Fit's thrilling for us."
OL,15,FGoldstein's message to Arthur ahead of
OL,16,Fhis quarter-finals appearance is to
OL,17,F"Keep it rolling."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
